snippet.title: Bravery Network Online Announcement - E3 2018
snippet.description:
A game by Gloam Collective

http://braverynetwork.online

Make friends, challenge strangers, 
& fight strategic turn-based battles 
in a post-post-apocalyptic world

CREDITS
Trailer by Derek Lieu & Min-Taylor Bai-Woo
Music by Jazz Mickle
